user_description: A proud Scot who now lives in England and who hopes the world becomes a better place. We shall see. Pacifist.
text: In view of the recent doubts around efficacy of the vaccines for Cancer sufferers undergoing Chemo, I am looking to get an antibody blood test to make sure I am safe. This service is not available for me at the moment, why? #CovidVaccine @MattHancock @NHSEngland

But Science is like this is always changing and is unpredictable that is its nature no doubt about that. I don't see how the cycle will end either you could die from the virus or from a vaccine. Living is a risk anyways be free and enjoy life do whatever you want!#CovidVaccine
